headline: Fastenal Company Announces Conference Call to Review 2025 First Quarter Earnings
summary: WINONA, Minn., March 27, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) (collectively referred to as 'Fastenal' or by terms such as 'we', 'our', or 'us') announced the date and time for its conference call to review 2025 first quarter results, as well as current operations. The conference call will be broadcast live over the Internet on Friday, April 11, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. central time.
